CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, November 9, 1957, pg. 4, reads: "Flooded Kitchen - The basement kitchen at 413 Third St., Rankin, is flooded so badly that Mrs. Henry and her seven children have to wait until the husband comes home at night in order to get a cooked meal. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Flooded basement kitchen of Henry residence, 413 Third Street, Rankin
